<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Reset - FiatFlex</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500;700&display=swap");

      * {
        font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .logo-wrap {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2em;
      }
      .otp-code {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 2px dashed #007bff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 300px;
      }
      .otp-number {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        color: #007bff;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .expiry-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666666;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4">
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px">
      <div class="logo-wrap">
        <img
          src="https://api.fiatflex.com/logo.png"
          alt="FiatFlex Logo"
          style="height: 60px"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 style="color: #272727">Password Reset Request</h1>

      <p style="color: #272727">
        You requested to reset your password. Please use the verification code
        below:
      </p>

      <div class="otp-code">
        <div class="otp-number"><%= otp %></div>
        <p class="expiry-text">This code expires in 15 minutes</p>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #666666; margin-top: 30px">
        <strong>Security Notice:</strong><br />
        • This code will expire in 15 minutes<br />
        • If you didn't request this, please ignore this email<br />
        • Never share this code with anyone
      </p>

      <p style="color: #666666">
        If you have any questions, just reply to this email—we're always happy
        to help out.
      </p>

      <p style="color: #666666">Cheers,<br />FIATFLEX TEAM</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
